<p>so close to the sea &amp; very sandy &amp; chalky.</p>
<p>It rained very heavy last night at times, hope it dosn't do the same tonight for some of us will be sleeping out.</p>
<p>It seems funny to hear the bugles calling again after being away for so long from them.</p>
<p>Sergt Major Pegg asked Len today if he would take on Company Q M for a while, if I was him I would grab it.</p>
<p>There are all sorts of hospitals here, including American, Canadian, English &amp; Australian. I believe the Yankie's are being recalled to America for they</p>
